ve that list (a =E2=80=9Cblock=E2=80=9D), and if they all agree then the bl=
ock is enshrined in the permanent ledger (the =E2=80=9Cblockchain=E2=80=9D)=
. We talked about this system last week, because some guys kind of hacked i=
