Everton football club bidder 777 Partners.The agency is arguing in a New Je=
rsey court that it has a First Amendment right to publish its opinion on a =
company=E2=80=99s financial strength, after two US insurers accused it of u=
sing=C2=A0=E2=80=9Cflawed methods, improper assumptions, and demonstrably f=
alse data=E2=80=9D to downgrade them.=E2=80=9CThe lifeblood of AM Best=E2=
=80=99s business is its credibility, and that credibility is irreparably da=
maged when it is prevented from publishing its opinions about an insurer=E2=
