ponse filed with the court this week.Here is the insurers=E2=80=99 lawsuit,=
 which argues that A.M. Best had a customer agreement with them =E2=80=94=
=C2=A0largely an implicit one, based on their past dealings, rather than an=
 actual written contract =E2=80=94=C2=A0that requires it to listen to their=
