cape is moving quickly, and the market deserves and needs to know AM Best=
=E2=80=99s current evaluation as to ACAP=E2=80=99s creditworthiness and abi=
lity to pay claims.=E2=80=9D This seems completely right! If you are a rati=
ngs agency, and you think that the creditworthiness of a company has declin=
