p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">All the stuff about keeping ledgers and voti=
ng sounds pretty active, but it doesn=E2=80=99t have to be. It is all algor=
ithmic and done by computers. And so there is a marketplace in which, essen=
tially, (1) I run computers to do the validating stuff, (2) you lend me you=
