th: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgrou=
nd-color: #ccc;">the insurers=E2=80=99 lawsuit</a>, which argues that A.M. =
Best had a customer agreement with them =E2=80=94=C2=A0largely an implicit =
one, based on their past dealings, rather than an actual written contract =
=E2=80=94=C2=A0that requires it to listen to their arguments and not act to=
o rashly. So, the insurers argue, the court should review A.M. Best=E2=80=
=99s decision to make sure it=E2=80=99s not cutting their ratings too hasti=
ly.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bl=
oombergbusiness.com/click/35478826.261334/aHR0cHM6Ly9hc3NldHMuYndieC5pby9kb=
