ottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid;=
 background-color: #ccc;">another=C2=A0letter</a> from A.M. Best filed yest=
erday, citing the Leadenhall lawsuit and saying that =E2=80=9Cthe landscape=
 is moving quickly, and the market deserves and needs to know AM Best=E2=80=
=99s current evaluation as to ACAP=E2=80=99s creditworthiness and ability t=
o pay claims.=E2=80=9D This seems completely right! If you are a ratings ag=
ency, and you think that the creditworthiness of a company has declined, yo=
u really do have to publish that! That is what the market expects of you; r=
